(6, 0, 1541084223, 1541084223, 0, 0, 'Sri Manchala ', '<p>Sri Manchala</p><p>Chairman, Trasers</p><p>Founder - Trianz; Cisco Systems; KPMG; Indian Army</p><p>San Francisco Bay Area</p><p>Summary</p><p>Sri Manchala is the founder of Trasers- a business research organization dedicated to developing fact based insights on digital and business transformations across industries. Throughout 2017 and 2018, Trasers conducted the worlds largest survey on digital transformations which received responses from over 9,200 leaders from 5,000+ companies across 16 industries. Trasers is an independent organization provides research and advisory services to clients in understanding transformations, benchmarking their organizations, developing their transformation strategies and priorities using fact based insights.</p><p>Sri carries over 30 years of experience in leadership, strategy and execution and two plus decades of experience in the technology industry. As the founder of technology strategy, consulting and implementation services firm- TRIANZ, Sri brings over18 years of CEO experience and perspectives, client success and business impact to Trasers. TRIANZ is focused on helping leadership develop strategies to transition into a Digital Enterprise leveraging digitalization, analytics, cloud infrastructures and security.</p><p>Sri\'s personal passion for leadership, strategy, execution and results began early in his career. As a graduate of the elite National Defense Academy and the Indian Military Academy, Sri was commissioned as an officer into the Indian Army. He was a Major and has served in the Infantry and a Special Forces unit of the Parachute Regiment.</p><p>Joining the industry in 1994 Sri had a short stint at Asian Paints, India\'s largest paints manufacturer. After his MBA, Sri worked with KPMG in Silicon Valley and later had a stint at Cisco Systems at the company\'s headquarters in the information technology division.</p><p>Sri serves on the Board of Advisors of the Marshall School of Business at the University of Southern California, Los Angeles. Sri has been a soccer player, an athlete and is a keen sports enthusiast. Sri and his family live in the Silicon Valley.<br /><br />   <img src=\"https://stgplus.trasers.com/image_transcoder.php?o=bx_froala_image&amp;h=15&amp;dpx=2&amp;t=1541083788\" style=\"width:448px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" alt=\"image_transcoder.php?o=bx_froala_image&amp;h=15&amp;dpx=2&amp;t=1541083788\" /></p><p></p>', '', '0000-00-00', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
