(521, 'sys_about', 1, 'system', 'about block 1', '_sys_block_type_html_1546592740', 13, 2147483647, '0', 'html', '<p>As the leader of an organization, CEOs and C-Suite executives need to respond to digital age challenges and develop future leadership skills to build organization culture that fosters and accelerates digital transformation. So, what steps do you need to take to drive digital transformation?</p><p>Trasers+ is a true business-to-business collaborative network for leaders and decision makers aimed at reinventing transformation by exchanging leading edge insights and practices and innovative ideas. Our forum enables the members to share insights on latest technologies, industry trends and innovative ideas in a non-competitive environment.&nbsp;</p><p>At Trasers+, we offer you an opportunity to interact, engage and build lasting relationships with hundreds of like-minded leaders from a range of industries by discussing the business challenges and sharing insights and experiences on their journey of digital transformation. Our vision is to offer a collaborative networking platform for leaders with a purpose of fostering a collaborative dialogue, promoting out-of-the-box thinking, and leadership development and mutual support.</p><p>Trasers+ is an invitation only membership platform and accepts membership from Directors and above who are committed to driving digital transformation. No matter where you are on your digital transformation journey, visit Trasers+ and discover why it is your go to place to thrive and succeed in the digitally transformative world.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0),
(518, 'bx_groups_view_profile', 2, 'system', '_sys_block_type_service_1541472209', '_sys_block_type_service_1541472209_1546585916', 11, 2147483647, '0', 'service', 'a:3:{s:6:\"module\";s:10:\"bx_trasers\";s:6:\"method\";s:20:\"browse_joined_groups\";s:6:\"params\";a:0:{}}', 1, 0, 1, 11),
(522, 'sys_about', 1, 'system', 'about block 2', '', 11, 2147483647, '0', 'html', '<p>Whether youve built your company from ground up, taken it to new heights through a transformation or gearing up for the start-up grind, youve already made a mark. But youre hungry for more&nbsp;</p><p>Trasers+, a community of transformation leaders at the top and like-minded decision makers offers you all of that  a strong foundation, a trusted peer group, wisdom and inspiration. You will get a chance to interact with other leaders in transformation industry, share your story, opinions and problems. The credits earned through your participation can be converted into benefits such as access to all groups and Trasers exclusive insights and reports.</p><p>Look at what Trasers+ membership can mean to your professional journey.</p><p><strong>Network, network and network</strong></p><p>Networking is the key to everything. Trasers+ offers you access to the right entrepreneur, the right marketer, the right technologist and more. Networking on Trasers+ will not only give you exposure to new perspectives, but also access to stories and insights shared by other transformation leaders. Join Trasers+ to develop authentic mentoring relationships and build your knowledge that would be instrumental in helping you grow your business.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Grow your business&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Apple took 42 years to become the worlds first trillion-dollar public company while Pinterest took just 2.46 years to reach a valuation of $1 billion. Whatever, your business is, every great idea seems implausible at first. Trasers+ community of leaders will provide that much-needed feedback to transform your seemingly far-fetched idea into a breakthrough one. Learn hacks to raise money, manage cash flow, build sales channels, or hire the best talent to take your company to the next level in your digital transformation journey.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Learn from the experts</strong></p><p>Have you ever found yourself bogged down due to management or business challenges? At Trasers+, you will find a group of mentors who will help you achieve high growth by offering innovative solutions to complex problems.</p><p>Our knowledge-sharing community is at your disposal to help you at every step of the way and focused on your success.</p><p><strong>Build online reputation</strong></p><p>It will get your and your companys name out there. Frequent interactions with the community will also help you build your online reputation and trusted connections. Your contribution and participation will help you earn credits that can be converted into benefits in form of access to all groups, exclusive insights and reports, and options to upgrade from amateur to pro.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 2),
(523, 'sys_about', 1, 'system', 'about block 3', '', 11, 2147483647, '0', 'html', '<p>Transforming organizations require articulated aspirations, as well as the ability to generate new ideas, collaborate, and learn from the constant churn. Trasers+ offers you a medium to do all this and more.&nbsp;</p><p>Your contribution and participation will help you earn credits that can be converted into benefits in form of access to all groups, exclusive insights and reports, and options to upgrade from amateur to pro.</p><p>Find below few tips that can help you move from amateur to pro and gain access to all the benefits.</p><p><strong>Spot that roadblock</strong></p><p>Have you wondered why few companies fail to unleash their full potential? Its because they fail to identify the barriers holding innovation back. Spur your business growth by sharing your problems with like-minded transformation leaders and getting solutions.</p><p><strong>Let your creative juices flow</strong></p><p>Have your freely shared that one cool idea you got one night from churning around those abstract brainstorms for critical transformation challenges? Here, you can share your radical ideas and develop it further with the expertise of Trasers+ members.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Share your drive for radical change</strong></p><p>Have you ever driven radical change in your organization? Share your success story on Trasers+ and inspire the community.</p><p><strong>Mentor others</strong></p><p>Nothing is ever perfect, but constant improvements can take an innovative idea to near-perfection. Do you have the drive to help individuals make things better? Comment, ask, collaborate; make your contributions matter.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 3),
(526, 'Help', 1, 'custom', '', '_sys_block_type_raw_1546602964', 0, 2147483647, '0', 'raw', '<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>Dos and donts for Trasers+</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Trasers+ is a collaborative platform for  digital transformation leaders to interact, engage and build lasting  relationships with like -minded people. Its important to follow a set of dos and donts, so we all may continue to enjoy Trasers+  for what it is.</p>\r\n<p><b style=\"color:#01669c\">Top  10 Dos </b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Do  introduce yourself on Trasers+ profile page when you register.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  become a valued contributor to the site by interacting with other members, sharing  best practices, ideas, posting comments, participating in polls, or asking your  own.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  read community guidelines before making a submission.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  ensure your message adheres to the topic, while being engaging, and innovative. </li>\r\n  <li>Do  attribute the social media or portfolio link to the author/ creator if youre  posting someone elses work.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  appreciate and encourage diverse viewpoints.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  provide constructive feedback to posts/ideas floated in the community.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  use link shorteners to post your content.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  report any spam you find.</li>\r\n  <li>Do  contact Trasers+ admin/moderator, if youve any doubts or you wish to report  about the content posted on the site.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b style=\"color:#01669c\">Top  10 Donts </b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Dont  self-promote, or post promotional messages about your product or service if it  doesnt relate to the topic at hand. </li>\r\n  <li>Dont  ignore criticism related to your posts and make the attack personal; focus on  the arguments. </li>\r\n  <li>Dont  share posts that could be deemed as objectionable to the larger group. </li>\r\n  <li>Dont  post someones personal information or post links to personal information. </li>\r\n  <li>Dont  encourage opinions or perspectives only from one group or member. </li>\r\n  <li>Dont  encourage bigotry or be disrespectful to other community members.</li>\r\n  <li>Dont  engage in trolling.</li>\r\n  <li>Dont  report posts or content based on your personal like or dislike. Report only if  it doesnt conform to community guidelines.</li>\r\n  <li>Dont  encourage or send out personal messages asking members to like or comment on  your content. </li>\r\n  <li>Dont  post comments like lol, rofl that dont add anything to the discussion. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I update my profile page? </strong>\r\n<p>  Whether you are trying to get more exposure  online or connect with peers, there is no better personal or brand landing page  than your profile page. A well-thought-out  profile page not just builds your online reputation but also pushes you far  ahead in search rankings.</p>\r\n<p>  Building a solid Trasers + profile is easy.  Just click on the button. Here you can follow the steps to complete  your profile. We know this sounds exhausting, but dont be alarmed. We value  your privacy and will never share your details with any third party. </p>\r\n<p>  You have complete control over how much and  with whom you choose to share your data. </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>   Upload  your picture: Adding a picture to your profile page increases your profile  visibility by 10x. For good results, its recommended that you use a professional  photo that shows your face clearly. Refrain from using any natural  surroundings, animals, inanimate objects or popular celebrity icons as your  profile image.</li>\r\n  <li> Full  Name: Adding your complete name sounds professional and makes it easier for  people to search you. We recommend you use your complete name in your profile.</li>\r\n  <li> Designation:  Adding a designation brings more flavor to your profile and helps you as well  as people to make connections easily. It makes you stand out in the crowd and  enables like-minded people to approach.</li>\r\n  <li> Industry:  An industry description helps people to narrow the search and makes you stand  out in the crowd. It also helps us to connect your profile with other profiles  in our database.</li>\r\n  <li> Location  (Country/Region) (Province/ State)  Again, updating your country, region in  your profile page helps narrow and refine search results. It will help you  connect with regional Traserites for live interactions. </li>\r\n  <li> Profile  summary: Your profile summary is the most important real estate to make your  profile stand out. Keep it short (300 words max.) and professional, and ensure  you highlight your skills, achievements, and expertise. This is how connections  will reach out to you for any networking or business opportunities. Its better  if you write in first person as it sounds more personal.</li>\r\n  <li> Company  website: We recommend you list your company website as it gives people a chance  to visit and know more about your business. It will also help you in getting  more traffic and networking opportunities in similar industry.</li>\r\n  <li> Social  Media: You can also add your social media details to your profile, which will  help you in growing your professional network. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>What  can I see on the Activity page?</strong>\r\n<p>  Your Activity page shows all the activities  and updates you share from your Trasers+ account. It could be an article, a  simple update or a teaser video. By default, your activity will be visible to  all the other members, but you can also choose who can see or receive your  updates by modifying the settings.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>What  can I expect to see on my feed?</strong>\r\n<p>  Your feed page will have a mix of  professional and personalized content. It will have posts from your network,  updates or content from the companies you follow. Occasionally you might also  see some posts that we think might interest you. You can always choose to  control and customize your feed.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  do I share a post, video or an update?</strong>\r\n<p>Sharing a post or an update is simple on  Trasers+. Just click on Add New button on the Trasers+ home page as soon as  you login and then select Article, Post, or Video. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I modify the notifications being sent to me?</strong>\r\n<p>  You can also sort your updates in the order  you want in your feed on the home page. By default, the feed is set to the Top  Updates, which is selected according to relevance, based on your activity. You  can also change it to the Recent Updates, which are organized chronologically.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  do I search on Trasers+?</strong>\r\n<p>  You can search for people, posts,  companies, groups from the search bar on top of the Trasers+ home page.  Additional search filters are also available on the right side of the home page  where you can search for the most active discussions on the trending topics or  articles. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>Can  I change my privacy settings?</strong>\r\n<p>  Yes. We value your privacy and you can  choose to modify it anytime via the settings section in the drop down from your  name on the top right corner of your home page. Change the privacy settings by  checking the relevant boxes. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I flag inappropriate content?</strong>\r\n<p>Your Trasers+ feed will have updates from  your network or the companies you follow. If you find any content that doesnt  conform to our guidelines, you can bring it to our moderators notice by  flagging it.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I follow/unfollow people or companies?</strong>\r\n<p>You can add people/companies to your  network and start receiving their content in your feed. You can also choose to  just unfollow anyone and remain connected to them. The only difference would be  you will no longer see their content in your feed.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I send a direct message to anyone?</strong>\r\n<p>You can send a direct message only to the  people who accept your request to send them messages via the messaging button  on the black bar under your name on the home page. You can choose to add people  to your network and once they accept their request, they become your  connections. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I chat with my connections?</strong>\r\n<p>  You can chat with your connections through  the messenger section under your name on the top right corner of your home  page. Just click on the connection name and chat on!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>What  should I do if I need further support?</strong>\r\n<p>We offer a dedicated 24x7 help desk to sort  out any concerns related to the website. You can chat with Darwin, our bot for  quick responses to your issues. You can also call the number shared on the top  right side of the home page and share your concerns with our reps. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I offer feedback?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Your feedback is important to us as it  helps us improve. Please drop us a line about your experiences at.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>Where  can I see my connection network?</strong>\r\n<p>You can see all your connections under the  friends section under your name on the top right corner of your home page.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>What  does the notifications section do?</strong>\r\n<p>The notifications tab under your name on  the top right corner of your home page lists all the activities on your post  while you were away. You can check what your connections have posted or  commented on your posts, even updates from your company networks.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I participate in community discussions?</strong>\r\n<p>You can participate in discussions via the  forums button on the solid bar under your name on the home page. You can also  search for specific topics or discussion threads under the search filter  inside. This forum also allows you to start a new thread on an area of your interest.  Post a question, share a new industry trend, an idea, or a video on the forum. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>What  can I see in the dash button?</strong>\r\n<p>The dash button under your name on the top  right corner of the home page is the place where you can see the analytics of all  your activities in one place.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block1-item\">\r\n<strong>How  can I join a Group?</strong>\r\n<p>  You can be a part of various groups in the  Trasers+ community. Under the Groups section on the left navigation bar of the  Forum page, you will find various groups listed. Just choose one as per your  interest and start your discussions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script src=\"/modules/boonex/trasers/js/faq.js\"></script>', 1, 1, 1, 2),
(569, 'bx_groups_fans', 2, 'system', '', '_sys_page_block_title_profile_stats_1546682077', 13, 2147483644, '', 'service', 'a:4:{s:6:\"module\";s:6:\"system\";s:6:\"method\";s:13:\"profile_stats\";s:6:\"params\";a:0:{}s:5:\"class\";s:20:\"TemplServiceProfiles\";}', 1, 0, 1, 0),
(527, 'Help', 2, 'custom', '', '_sys_block_type_raw_1546603022', 13, 2147483647, '0', 'raw', '<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block2\">\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block2-header\">\r\n  Contribution guidelines\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bx-page-faq-block2-intro\">\r\n	<p>Trasers+  is all about driving productive conversations and exchanging ideas. To help you  make the most of it, here are a set of guidelines.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>Dont hold back</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trasers+  is designed to facilitate an exchange of innovative ideas, and we all know  innovation can come across as unusual, unconventional, crazy. As Larry Page  once said, Good ideas are always crazy until they are not. So, dont hold  back, challenge the unorthodox, and help propel the businesses to become more  adaptable, innovative, and engaging. </p>\r\n<p><strong>KISS</strong></p>\r\n<p>Or  keep it short and simple as they call it! After all, so many things are vying  for everyones attention these days. Stay focused on your main idea and include  all the essential details. Also, refrain from sharing any third-party  commercial link or URL.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Avoid self-promotion</strong></p>\r\n<p>You  are most welcome to share content or ideas from your website or blog. But we expect you to be mindful of the fine line between  talking with people and talking at them. As we said, great conversation and  exchange of ideas are vital for Trasers+ community.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Invite collaboration</strong></p>\r\n<p>Innovation  doesnt happen in a vacuum. We encourage you to invite suggestions from the  group to help you advance your ideas. At the same time, you must also reciprocate.  After all, a community is all about bringing people together in ways that allow  them to do things they couldn\'t have done in isolation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Be inclusive</strong></p>\r\n<p>Diversity  fuels innovation. Sometimes, different perspectives can bring a sense of discomfort.  Encourage all voices, help new perspectives be heard, listen actively, and keep  the discussion respectful. Value others ideas, styles, and viewpoints.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Be pragmatic </strong></p>\r\n<p>We  understand your enthusiasm to bounce ideas off in the group but ensure to back  them up with data. In complex stream of conversations, sometimes its difficult  to gauge the difference between ideas born out of learning, and that of pure  fantasy (not to say that fantasy isnt constructive; after all, someone did  think of flying objects and then the airplane was invented!). Structure your  idea to gain traction within the community.</p>\r\n<p><strong>No inappropriate content </strong></p>\r\n<p>  As  a community, its important that we maintain a sense of decorum and respect  within the group. We urge you to refrain from posting any content that could be  deemed as inappropriate including religious, political, offensive, misleading,  fraudulent, threatening, defamatory, illegal or discriminatory. After all,  happy communities are thriving communities! </p>\r\n</div>', 1, 1, 1, 0),
