(2005, 'bx_invites_invite', 2, 'custom', '', '_sys_block_type_raw_1556531942', 11, 2147483647, '0', 'raw', '<p class=\'bx-page-about-header\' style=\'margin-top:0px; padding-top:0px;\'> Spread the Word! </p>\r\n        <p class=\'bx-def-font\'>\r\n        We appreciate the time and efforts you put in to share tips, collaborate, and give that much-needed boost to individuals on Trasers+. However, Communities are more fun with more people around to share your stories. Do you have friends or colleagues who would love us? Refer them to Trasers+. </p>\r\n\r\n       <p class=\'bx-def-font\'>\r\n        Every time you bring someone along for a ride, well credit points and goodies to you! Trasers+ credits are just one of the little ways we try to give back to you. These credits give you access to exclusive benefits. You can view and use your Trasers+ points from your account settings.</p>  \r\n        <p class=\'bx-def-font\'> \r\n        Tell us about your referrals by filling out the details here. Submit their details and we will keep you posted when they join the network!</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0),
