(762, 'bx_events_calendar', 2, 'custom', '', '_sys_block_type_raw_1555586820', 11, 2147483647, '0', 'raw', '<div class=\"bx-form-input-wrapper bx-form-input-wrapper-text bx-form-input-wrapper-search\" style=\"background:#f1f1f1 !important;\">\r\n<i class=\"sys-icon search\"></i>\r\n<form id=\"sys_search_form_quick\" action=\"/searchKeyword.php\" method=\"post\" class=\"bx-form-advanced\" style=\"display: inline-block; background:#f1f1f1 !important;\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"live_search\" value=\"1\" class=\"bx-def-font-inputs bx-form-input-hidden\">\r\n<input placeholder=\"Event\"  background:#f1f1f1 !important;\r\nonkeypress=\"return bx_search_on_type(event, 5, \'#sys_search_form_quick\', \'#sys_search_results_quick\', \'#sys_search_results_quick\', \'1\');\" \r\nonpaste=\"return bx_search_on_type(event, 5, \'#sys_search_form_quick\', \'#sys_search_results_quick\', \'#sys_search_results_quick\', \'1\');\" \r\ntype=\"text\" name=\"keyword\" value=\"\" class=\"bx-def-font-inputs bx-form-input-text bx-event-form-input-text-search\">\r\n</form>\r\n                </div>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n\r\nTrasers+ events are an exclusive space where industry leaders come together to collaborate, innovate, and discover the strategic ways to do more with digital transformation.  </br> </br>\r\nBe it conferences, symposiums, trade shows & expos, or breakfast sessions  Trasers+ host a variety of events designed to help you navigate your pressing digital transformation challenges, right from transforming the current landscape to setting up businesses for future growth.  </br></br>\r\n\r\nSo, whether you are facing budgetary constraints, having troubles with inter-team collaboration, legacy IT architecture, or you simply dont know where to begin  Trasers+ events will get you the required expert peer intelligence to enhance your digital leadership.  </br> </br>\r\n\r\nHere, you are in charge! You can propose to set up workshops, volunteer for seminars, and conduct deep-dive speaking sessions on niche topics you care about - among other things  seizing an opportunity to drive the industry landscape with inspirational content and ideas. </br> </br>\r\n\r\nRegister and join Trasers+ events to get access to thought-provoking speakers and influential peers and leverage digital advancements shaping the future of business in an intimate environment.  </br> </br>\r\n', 1, 1, 1, 2),
