(2040, 'Merit', 1, 'custom', '', '_sys_block_type_raw_1566278183', 11, 2147483647, '0', 'raw', '<span>\r\nTrasers+ credits are just one of the little ways we try to give back to you. These credits give you access to exclusive benefits. Here are just a few ways through which you can earn credits:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">\r\nCreate forums:</spam> Earn credits by creating private events and discussion forums, moderating and leading the discussions on the same\r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Contribute (blogs, articles):</spam> You can earn Trasers+ credits by frequently participating in meaningful conversations that are useful for the community. For each content contribution, you are eligible to earn credits based on their ratings and as decided by the algorithm. \r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Create idea groups: </spam>Create idea groups and share innovative ideas with like-minded people on Ideate link. More participation in your idea groups mean having those extra eyeballs that will get more traffic to your idea as well as interactions on our platform; its a win-win for both of us. But you get to earn extra credits.\r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Provide help: </spam>Play the role of the mentor, guide and provide help to other traserites. The more you attract followers to seek help from you, the more credits you earn. \r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Refer a friend:</spam> Communities are more fun with more people around to share your stories. Every time you bring someone along for a ride, well credit points and goodies to you!\r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Suggest Trasers research agenda:</spam> Earn credits by leveraging your experience in digital transformation to suggest topics for syndicated reports of Trasers. \r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Participate in Poll:</spam> Polls are the channels to record your votes and opinions on a particular topic. Earn credits by participating in polls posted on the Trasers+ website and letting us know your opinion on the same. \r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Case studies of self-innovation: </spam>One of the objectives of Trasers+ is to help our members drive thought leadership by sharing their innovations and stories with like-minded people. And you earn extra credits. \r\n</li><li><spam class=\"eventdetailshead\">Leadership interviews: </spam>You will get extra credits each time you volunteer to participate in leadership interviews. Remember, more interviews mean more followers, increased traffic, meaningful insights, great ideas, even!\r\n</li>\r\n</ul> \r\n<span>Watch out this space for more shortly.</span>', 1, 1, 0, 0),
